    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roll the dice to feed a hungry vampire. Buy items, upgrade multipliers, discover remnants of the past, and make the right choices to survive the mansion. Will you meet the quota set upon you, or will you succumb to fate?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Modify rooms for some crazy loot but at the cost of a higher difficulty.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129330/extras/b51d9df2984e937b8224ab4d16d66e4c.avif?t=1771799521\" width=1560 height=874 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roll the dice to satisfy the quota and earn money.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129330/extras/8b8b3acf25cde418163b168494c55e11.avif?t=1771799521\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spend that money to unlock items and quest items that will help you on your run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129330/extras/fb1b9c39bba280869abb4eecc5579b80.avif?t=1771799521\" width=1560 height=876 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make it out to tell others of the tale and live on for those that perished.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This and much more to come in development! </p>",
